    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-11-28T09:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-11-28T09:00:00-05:00" n="527"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d527">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">683.84A/11–2852: Telegram</note>
                <head>No. 527<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Syria (<persName corresp="#p_MJS1"
                            type="from">Moose</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Department of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d527fn1">Repeated to Tel Aviv, Paris, Amman, Baghdad,
                        Beirut, Cairo, London, Rome, Ankara, and Jidda.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Damascus</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1952-11-28T16:00:00+02:00"
                            >November 28, 1952—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>386. Tel Aviv tel 779 to Dept Nov 13. Emb does not accept implication <gloss
                        target="#t_reftel1">reftel</gloss> that progress toward area stability and
                    attainment mutually satisfactory Syro-Israel <hi rend="italic">modus
                        vivendi</hi> only possible if Syria envisions negots as directed toward
                    peace. Proposal divide demil zone on <hi rend="italic">de facto</hi> basis
                        (<gloss target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 345, Nov 6) wld, if adopted,
                    increase area stability by reducing Syro-Israel border tensions, and wld also
                    build confidence for future more general arrangements. Wld not satisfy main
                    Israel aims, but only way ultimately reestablish Syro-Israel peace and
                    commercial relations is by several successive steps of which creation <hi
                        rend="italic">de facto</hi> frontier wld appear to be first. As such, <hi
                        rend="italic">modus vivendi</hi> wld be step toward peace whether or not so
                    regarded by Syrians.</p>
                <p>Initiative now with Israel for renewal contacts fol Oct 9 mtg (<gloss
                        target="#t_Embtel1">Embtel</gloss> 354, Nov 12).</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <persName corresp="#p_MJS1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Moose</hi>
                        </persName>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
